snippet.title: 【Project MIKHAIL】Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the Early Access Launch trailer for the Tactial Surface Fighter Battle Action Game "Project MIKHAIL", out 11/2/2021 on Steam!
Store Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1557480/Project_MIKHAIL_A_MuvLuv_War_Story/

We hope you'll play it and give us your feedback!
On sale in Early Access now!

Join the Official Discord: https://discord.gg/ng8b8qqDFk

Links:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/ProjectMIKHAIL
Official Site: https://project-mikhail.com/en
Anime (Airing Fall 2021!): https://muv-luv-alternative-anime.com/

#ProjectMIKHAIL
#Muvluv
